
<div class="offset1 span4">

    <div class ="notice_board">

      <%= form_for(@wolf) do |f| %>

        <%= render 'shared/error_messages' , object: f.object%>

              <i class="press icon-file-alt icon-3x pull-left icon-muted"></i>
              <div class="titlearea">
                    <h2>Write a description</h2>
              </div>

              <%= f.text_field :title, class: "input", placeholder: "Add a title in less than 140 characters" %>
              <%= f.text_area :content, rows: "30", cols: "14", class: "redactor", placeholder: "when/where/what/do not leave contact information here/put reward in separate row" %>
              
              <i class="press icon-magnet icon-3x pull-left icon-muted"></i>
              <div class="titlearea">
                    <h2>Put up a reward</h2>
              </div>

              <%= f.text_field :reward, class: "input", placeholder: "$500 or 500 free beer" %>

              <i class="press icon-qrcode icon-3x pull-left icon-muted"></i>
              <div class="titlearea">
                    <h2>Generate the token</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="buttomcontainer">
              <%= f.submit "Generate Search Token", class: "buttom"%>
              </div>

      <% end %>

    </div>

</div>



<div class="offset1 span4">

    <div class ="notice_board">


              <div class="wraparound">
                <i class="press icon-bullhorn icon-3x pull-left"></i>
                <p class="lead">Call up your friends to help <%=current_user.name%> and earn the reward togather</p>
                <h4 class="pull-right">Reward is <div style="display:inline" id="reward"></div></h4>
              </div>
              <br>
              <br>
              <br>
              <div class="message">

                <h4><div id ="title"></div></h4>
                <br><br>

                <div id ="content"></div>

              </div>

              <i class="press icon-qrcode icon-3x pull-left icon-muted"></i>

              <div class="titlearea">
                    <h2>QR code</h2>
              </div>


              <div class="qrcode">
                <i class="press icon-qrcode icon-4x" style="padding-right:0"></i>
              </div>

              <i class="press icon-info-sign icon-3x pull-left icon-muted"></i>

              <div class="titlearea">
                    <h2>How does it work</h2>
              </div>


              <div class= "howto">
                <p></p>
                <p class="lead">Reward allocation</p>

                <p> Say the reward is $1000. If you help to send the request to John, and John signed up and twitted it to his friend Roland and (finger crossed) Roland found what <%=current_user.name%> were looking for (hooray!). Roland will receive $500, John will receive $250 and you will recieve $120. </p>

                <br>

                <p class="lead">Spread the words</p>


                <p> Help to get the message out on facebook, twitter, email, blog, craigslist.</p>
                <p> Inludes this link  <code> to be generated </code> and state the reward. </p>
                <p> Or you can simply print out this page and post it somewhere, the QRcode is the link to your page </p> <br>


                <p class="lead">Monitor the progress</p>


                <p> After you sent out invitations, you can monitor the development of your network from your home page. </p>
                <p> If someone in your network submit a lead, the whole team of helpers lead up to that person will be informated. Everyone will able to vote on the lead according to its relevance.</p>

                <br><br>
                <div class="poster">

                <i class="press icon-bullhorn icon-2x pull-left"></i>
                <p class="lead">“Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance, you must keep moving.” </p>



                </div>


              </div>

    </div>

</div>



<script>

$("#wolf_title").keyup(function() {
    console.log("key");
    $("#title").html(this.value);
});
$("#wolf_title").blur(function() {
    $("#title").html(this.value);
});

window.setInterval(function(){
  // keep content in sync
  $("#content").html($("#wolf_content").val());
}, 2000);

$("#wolf_reward").keyup(function() {
    $("#reward").html(this.value);
});
$("#wolf_reward").blur(function() {
    $("#reward").html(this.value);
});


</script>
